<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>LMS Activation Email</title>

    <style type="text/css">
        /* Base */
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            min-width: 100%;
            font-family: Arial sans-serif;
            font-family: 16px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            background-color: white;
            color: #222222;
        }

        a {
            color: #000;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            list-style: 1.25;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        p {
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 24px;
        }

        table td {
            vertical-align: top;
        }

        /* layout */
        .email-wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .email-header {
            background-color: #0070f3;
            padding: 24px;
            color: white;
        }

        .email-body {
            padding: 24px;
            background-color: white;
        }

        .email-footer {
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            padding: 24px;
        }

        /* buttons */
        .button {
            display: inline;
            background-color: #0070f3;
            color: white;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-align: center;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 12px 24px;
            border-radius: 4px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
        <div class="email-header">
            <h1>Welcome to Gohackathon LMS</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="email-body">
            <p>Hello <%= user.name %>, </p>
            <p>Thank you for registering with Gohackathon. To activate your account, please use the following activation code:</p>
            <h2><%= activationCode %></h2>
            <p>Please enter this code on the activation page within the next 5 minutes</p>
            <p>If you did not register for Gohackathon account, please ignore this email</p>
        </div>
        <div class="email-footer">
            <p>If you have any question, Please don't hesitate to contact us at <a href="mailto:info@gohackathon.in">info@gohackathon.in</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>